35:51.800 --> 35:54.560
'..it has since undergone
extensive renovations,

35:54.560 --> 35:58.560
'and in the late
'40s became a public hospital.'

35:59.480 --> 36:03.480
You know, when I was in recovery,
I had this hallucination,

36:03.640 --> 36:07.240
you taking off the dressing, and
the bandages just kept unravelling

36:07.240 --> 36:09.720
and unravelling
and I kept telling you to hurry up,

36:09.720 --> 36:13.000
but the more you tried to hurry,
the more they unravelled.

36:13.000 --> 36:17.000
There were these heaps of bandages
piled up all over the floor.

36:17.440 --> 36:21.440
Almost done.

36:25.160 --> 36:26.240
There.

36:26.240 --> 36:29.480
I want you to keep it
immobile for at least a week.

36:29.480 --> 36:30.680
When can I go back to work?

36:30.680 --> 36:31.320
We'll see.

36:31.320 --> 36:32.720
We'll see.

36:32.720 --> 36:36.720
Helen, for once,
give yourself some time.

36:49.280 --> 36:53.280
The colour's excellent.
So is the size and symmetry.

36:53.320 --> 36:57.320
There's a little bruising but...

36:57.680 --> 37:00.160
I want to see it.

37:00.160 --> 37:01.200
Alone.

37:01.200 --> 37:02.440
Alone.

37:02.440 --> 37:04.800
I'll be back in a few minutes to
put on a new dressing.

37:04.800 --> 37:08.800
Thanks, Bobby.

37:09.000 --> 37:13.000
HE CLEARS THROAT

37:36.720 --> 37:38.240
KNOCK ON DOOR

37:38.240 --> 37:42.240
It's open.

37:48.680 --> 37:49.880
Something you want?

37:49.880 --> 37:51.320
Something you want?

37:51.320 --> 37:54.000
I know what you're going to say
but you don't have to worry.

37:54.000 --> 37:57.320
I promise, no more Mr Entertainment.

37:57.320 --> 38:01.320
I'm going to go back
and be my old self, Lyle Brubaker.

38:02.640 --> 38:04.560
You told me that before.

38:04.560 --> 38:08.080
I know but this time it's different.

38:08.080 --> 38:10.120
It's different.

38:10.120 --> 38:13.800
I swear on the grave
of Billie Holiday.

38:13.800 --> 38:14.920
I don't know.

38:14.920 --> 38:16.440
I don't know.

38:16.440 --> 38:18.800
I'll concentrate,
I'll do what I'm told.

38:18.800 --> 38:21.600
Please.

38:21.600 --> 38:25.600
Please.

38:25.640 --> 38:29.640
You are a good worker
when you concentrate.

38:30.760 --> 38:32.000
OK.

38:32.000 --> 38:34.280
Thanks, Mr Morgan, thank you.

38:34.280 --> 38:36.360
But...no singing!

38:36.360 --> 38:38.080
Under any circumstances.

38:38.080 --> 38:41.960
Not a note, not a rest, not a G-clef.

38:41.960 --> 38:44.480
Tomorrow morning, first thing, up to
the solarium,

38:44.480 --> 38:45.960
you wash all the windows.

38:45.960 --> 38:48.000
Welcome back, Len.

38:48.000 --> 38:52.000
Solarium, first thing, right?

38:57.600 --> 39:00.080
Ellen. &gt;

39:00.080 --> 39:02.240
Ellen? &gt;

39:02.240 --> 39:03.280
Mark?

39:03.280 --> 39:06.880
Mark?

39:06.880 --> 39:07.920
Yes.

39:07.920 --> 39:11.920
Yes.

39:12.040 --> 39:14.400
Oh.

39:14.400 --> 39:18.040
Oh, Mark, where have you been?
It's almost 1.00.

39:18.040 --> 39:20.560
I told you,
I was going for a ride. &gt;

39:20.560 --> 39:23.880
When I hit New Hampshire,
I figured I should turn around. &gt;

39:23.880 --> 39:25.200
Any phone calls? &gt;

39:25.200 --> 39:26.840
Any phone calls? &gt;

39:26.840 --> 39:28.280
No calls? &gt;

39:28.280 --> 39:31.640
Well, my mother called.
She loved the show. So did I.

39:31.640 --> 39:35.080
Please, I don't need a lot of hollow
sentiments right now. &gt;

39:35.080 --> 39:39.080
Oh, honey,
despite what you may think,

39:39.360 --> 39:42.440
it was actually quite positive.

39:42.440 --> 39:44.560
I looked like a moron. &gt;

39:44.560 --> 39:46.280
You're too hyper-critical.

39:46.280 --> 39:47.680
Oh, really? &gt;

39:47.680 --> 39:51.440
Quote, Martinet, "primadonna."

39:51.440 --> 39:54.560
Quote, Martinet, "primadonna."

39:54.560 --> 39:57.120
Don't cloud the issue.

39:57.120 --> 40:00.280
&lt; You're too demanding, Mark.
Mostly of yourself.

40:00.280 --> 40:02.760
You were that way back at Penn too.

40:02.760 --> 40:05.520
WATER RUNNING

40:05.520 --> 40:09.520
Maybe that's why you're
so good at what you do.

40:10.880 --> 40:12.280
All I know for sure is

40:12.280 --> 40:15.520
that I fell in love with the biggest
hard-ass on campus.

40:15.520 --> 40:18.440
It's going to take a whole lot more
than a silly TV show

40:18.440 --> 40:22.120
to make me feel otherwise.

40:22.120 --> 40:25.840
Mark?

40:25.840 --> 40:28.920
Did you say something, honey?

40:28.920 --> 40:31.480
For crying out loud!

40:31.480 --> 40:33.400
Goodnight.

40:33.400 --> 40:35.840
Goodnight.

40:35.840 --> 40:38.120
Ellen.

40:38.120 --> 40:40.120
What?

40:40.120 --> 40:41.760
I love you too.

40:41.760 --> 40:45.760
(LAUGHING)

40:48.560 --> 40:52.560
CRASHING

40:52.640 --> 40:54.480
Excuse me.

40:54.480 --> 40:56.760
It's time for me
to wash the windows in here.

40:56.760 --> 40:59.240
Go ahead.

40:59.240 --> 41:01.040
Mr Entertainment.

41:01.040 --> 41:03.160
No, no.
I'm not Mr Entertainment any more.

41:03.160 --> 41:04.600
My name is Lyle Brubaker.

41:04.600 --> 41:08.600
I won't sing and I won't dance,
don't ask me.

41:08.760 --> 41:10.720
No, no, no, no.

41:10.720 --> 41:13.840
I gotta stop doing that
because I gotta do a good job

41:13.840 --> 41:17.840
and the only way to do a good job
is to concentrate on it.

41:23.480 --> 41:27.480
Frank and Sammy and Deano would
have done the same thing.

41:28.080 --> 41:30.400
You seem like a smart lady.

41:30.400 --> 41:32.960
If you'd had second billing to
a dancing donkey,

41:32.960 --> 41:34.800
could you have performed?

41:34.800 --> 41:36.760
What are you talking about?

41:36.760 --> 41:40.240
(CLEARING THROAT)

41:40.240 --> 41:42.080
Not being good enough.

41:42.080 --> 41:43.720
Why?

41:43.720 --> 41:46.920
(STARTS TO SING)
Because seasons change and so do I.

41:46.920 --> 41:49.400
You need not wonder why.

41:49.400 --> 41:50.680
No.

41:50.680 --> 41:51.920
(GROANING)

41:51.920 --> 41:55.200
I got to concentrate.

41:55.200 --> 41:57.320
I tried it and I failed.

41:57.320 --> 41:59.920
There, I said it.
Hate me if you want to.

41:59.920 --> 42:03.920
I don't hate you.
I barely know you.

42:04.320 --> 42:08.320
Well, back to washing windows
and sweeping floors.

42:11.400 --> 42:15.400
You know what it's like to
have no options?

42:15.400 --> 42:18.440
Yes, I do.
You'll get used to it.

42:18.440 --> 42:20.680
I don't like it.

42:20.680 --> 42:23.560
I don't like thinking
I'll always be an amateur.

42:23.560 --> 42:27.440
There's no higher goal to attain
than to make people happy.

42:27.440 --> 42:31.320
Your singing makes people happy.

42:31.320 --> 42:35.320
And you're still Mr Entertainment.

42:36.120 --> 42:39.240
I am?

42:39.240 --> 42:42.120
You still have your identity.

42:42.120 --> 42:44.840
You should be glad you have one.

42:44.840 --> 42:48.520
Mine was stolen.

42:48.520 --> 42:52.520
There is nothing safe in this
hospital!

42:52.880 --> 42:55.720
There was another woman on floor west
who had her purse taken.

42:55.720 --> 42:57.320
She was real upset about it

42:57.320 --> 43:00.800
and I told her the same thing I'm
going to tell you. Carry a wallet.

43:00.800 --> 43:03.240
What?

43:03.240 --> 43:04.560
It wasn't your fault.

43:04.560 --> 43:08.320
It was my fault. I...

43:08.320 --> 43:12.040
..tried to help him.

43:12.040 --> 43:16.040
How could he have done that to me?

43:16.320 --> 43:19.400
(SOBBING)

43:19.400 --> 43:22.440
Well, don't worry.

43:22.440 --> 43:26.440
Look, you can go to the DMV and get
a new license and don't forget...

43:27.120 --> 43:30.040
to cancel your credit cards.

43:30.040 --> 43:33.040
And don't follow leaders,
watch your parking meters.

43:33.040 --> 43:34.480
No.

43:34.480 --> 43:38.480
(SOBBING)

43:38.560 --> 43:40.560
And don't be sad.

43:40.560 --> 43:43.560
God, I wish it was that easy!

43:43.560 --> 43:44.640
I understand.

43:44.640 --> 43:45.680
I understand.

43:45.680 --> 43:47.720
I understand.

43:47.720 --> 43:51.720
Don't...be sad.

43:52.960 --> 43:54.440
You want to borrow some money?

43:54.440 --> 43:57.200
You can pay it back
whenever you want.

43:57.200 --> 43:58.960
No, thank you.

43:58.960 --> 44:02.960
That's what friends are for.

44:06.120 --> 44:10.120
Well, can I do something for you?

44:12.080 --> 44:15.440
Sing me a song.

44:15.440 --> 44:19.440
Please.

